graph LR
    CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator<br/>v1.12.0]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    CodeFlare -->|RayCluster CRD| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.1.0<br/>REQUIRED]
    CodeFlare -->|certificate mgmt| CertController[cert-controller<br/>Embedded<br/>REQUIRED]
    CodeFlare -->|controller library| AppWrapperLib[AppWrapper Library<br/>v0.30.0<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    CodeFlare -.->|workload scheduling| Kueue[Kueue<br/>v0.8.3<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Platform Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    CodeFlare -->|OAuth auth| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>OpenShift only]
    CodeFlare -->|service certs| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA<br/>OpenShift only]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|CRD watch| DSCInit[opendatahub-operator<br/>DSCInitialization CRD]

    %% Monitoring Integration
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes metrics| CodeFlare

    %% What depends on CodeFlare
    DataScientists[Data Scientists] -->|creates clusters| CodeFlare
    MLEngineers[ML Engineers] -->|creates AppWrappers| CodeFlare
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| CodeFlare

    %% Ray Ecosystem
    CodeFlare -->|creates/manages| RayClusters[Ray Clusters<br/>Distributed workloads]
    RayClusters -->|uses| KubeRay

    %% Kueue Integration Flow
    CodeFlare -->|creates| AppWrappers[AppWrapper Resources<br/>workload.codeflare.dev]
    AppWrappers -->|submitted to| Kueue
    Kueue -.->|updates status| CodeFlare

